Mixed Tape: Bobby Volume 1 is a surfing video dvd about world ranked #5, Bobby Martinez. The name "Mixed Tape" ties into Bobby's mix of Latin and American culture, his love for music and the consolidation of countless tapes of footage they have shot over the last year. The end result is an action packed surf movie of A+ surfing. The movie features Bobby surfing at home in Santa Barbara, away on the WCT, and at various pumping surf spots across the globe. The film also features a section of the Reef Team lighting it up together and plenty more. Directed by Pete Santa Maria and produced by Reef Entertainment, this is one of those surfing videos that is meant to get every surfer amped to go surfing.
